      <div class="text-left card-body">

          <h3 class="card-title text-center">Before the Game</h3>
          <hr>
          <ul class="card-text ">
            <li>Join the discord 15 minutes early</li>
            <li>Join the <b>Hangout</b> voice channel (ex. The Hoven)</li>

          </ul>
          <h3 class="card-title mt-4 text-center">How to join a game</h3>
          <hr>
          <ul class="card-text">
            <li>Search <b>custom lobbies</b> for Wecasual</li>
            <li>Join lobby <b>"Wecasual [Your Discord Room Name]"</b> (ex. Wecasual The Hoven)</li>
            <li>Lobby password: <b>wecasual2017</b></li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class = "text-center my-2">OR</h3>

          <div class="rounded my-3">
            <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mt-0">
              <li class="list-group-item p-0  text-center mt-0">
                <a class="m-3 pink-btn btn btn-primary mb-2 dropdown" href="#readBeforePlaying" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">
                  <h5 class = "mb-0">Join the Dota Channel<span class="down-caret"></span></h5>
                </a>

                <div class="text-left collapse card-body p-1" id="readBeforePlaying">
                  <hr>
                    <h4 class="card-title">In Dota, click the “CHANNELS” button.</h4>
                    <img class = "img-fluid" src="/images/text-channel-guide-box.png" alt="Click Channels image">
                    <h4 class="card-title mt-2">Click on the “USER” tab</h4>
                    <h4 class="card-title mt-2">Search for Wecasual and click Join(It should show up)</h4>
                    <img class = "img-fluid" src="/images/text-channel-guide-search.png" alt="Search channels image">
