            <li>Report a player for any false gg calls or excessive pauses<a href="/contact" target="_blank"> here</a></li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="card-title mt-4 text-center">After the game</h3>
          <hr>
          <ul class="card-text ">
            <li>Head back to the <b>Hangout</b> and chill!</li>
